## Summary

- Replace `to_array()` with `String::op_get` indexing in `is_identifier_literal` across 3 files (script_setup/utils, sfc/generics, template/parser), removing per-call array allocations
- Replace `pascal_case` `to_array()` with `String` indexing + `unsafe_substring`
- Use `.trim().is_empty()` instead of `.trim().length() == 0` to avoid intermediate `String` allocation when only checking emptiness (10+ sites across codegen, template, common)
- Guard `trim().to_string()` behind `is_empty()` check to skip allocation on empty chunks in hot scan loops

